Task: How to cache tokio_postgres::Client without closing the connection?

 <p>I'm writing a library for creating and dropping postgres databases. I use it in tests to spin up and tear down test databases. Here is a snippet that works (excuse the lack of sql sanitizing. it's only used by myself in tests):</p>
<pre class="lang-rs prettyprint-override"><code>use tokio_postgres::{Client, NoTls};

